clude required <output-dir> arg.\nRemove unused SKILL_DIR variable from bundle.sh.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>\n\n---------\n\nCo-authored-by: felix-srp <felix@serendipityone.com>\nCo-authored-by: Claude Opus 4.6 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>",
